Where did the raven find the cheese? // Où le corbeau a-t-il trouvé le fromage ?

How did the crow manage to steal the cheese? // Comment le corbeau réussi à voler le fromage ?

On which sensitive string did the fox lean to steal the cheese?
He has the idea of flattering it, especially on its beautiful song.
What are the arguments of the fox?
He compliments him on his voice, when he sings all the forest is under the spell.
He finally sings on the request of the fox and finally drops the cheese.

